---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const locale = 'en';
const currentPath = '/cgv';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms and Conditions | JANUS Linguistic Agency Lyon"
  description="General terms and conditions for training, interpreting and translation services at JANUS Linguistic Agency."
  locale={locale}
  currentPath={currentPath}
>
  <section class="bg-anthracite pt-32 pb-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-gold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-8 h-px bg-gold inline-block"></span>Contractual</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-light text-white mb-12">Terms and Conditions</h1>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">1. Scope</h2>
          <p>These Terms and Conditions apply to all services provided by <strong class="text-white">JANUS Agence Linguistique</strong> (Agata Mich, sole trader, Lyon, France): language training, interpreting, on-site support, translation and intercultural consulting. Any order implies unconditional acceptance of these terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">2. Quotes and Orders</h2>
          <p>All services are preceded by a free, no-obligation quote, valid for 30 days. An order is confirmed by returning the signed quote (or written confirmation by email) and, where applicable, payment of the deposit.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">3. Pricing</h2>
          <p>Prices are quoted in euros excluding VAT. The applicable VAT rate is that in force on the invoice date. JANUS reserves the right to modify its prices at any time; services ordered before any change are invoiced at the accepted quote rate.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-none">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span><span><strong class="text-white">Training:</strong> 30% deposit on order, balance on receipt of invoice (30-day payment term).</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span><span><strong class="text-white">Interpreting / on-site support:</strong> full payment 7 days before the assignment, unless otherwise agreed.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span><span><strong class="text-white">Translation:</strong> payment on delivery, 15-day term.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Payment by bank transfer (details on invoice). Late payment penalties of 3× the legal rate apply automatically, plus a flat-rate recovery fee of €40.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">5. Cancellation and Rescheduling</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 list-none">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span><span><strong class="text-white">Training:</strong> free cancellation up to 15 days before start. 15–7 days: 50% of total. Under 7 days: 100%.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold shrink-0">◆</span><span><strong class="text-white">Interpreting / on-site:</strong> free cancellation up to 10 days before. 10–3 days: 50%. Under 3 days: 100%.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Any reschedule requested less than 5 working days before the planned date incurs a rescheduling fee of 20% of the total amount.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">6. Client Obligations</h2>
          <p>The client undertakes to provide all information necessary for the proper delivery of services (training materials, glossaries, assignment context) within agreed timeframes. Any client-caused delay may result in an equivalent extension to the delivery deadline.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">7. Confidentiality</h2>
          <p>JANUS undertakes to maintain strict confidentiality over all information communicated in the course of its assignments. A non-disclosure agreement (NDA) can be signed on request before any sensitive assignment.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">8. Training — Qualiopi and Funding</h2>
          <p>JANUS holds Qualiopi certification (no. 84692002569), enabling training to be funded by skills operators (OPCOs), the CPF, France Travail and company training plans (PDC). JANUS assists clients with funding applications but cannot guarantee their approval, which depends on third-party organisations.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">9. Liability</h2>
          <p>JANUS undertakes to perform its services with all due care and diligence. Its liability is limited to the amount of the service in question. JANUS shall not be held liable for any commercial consequences arising from the outcome of negotiations in which it participated as interpreter or consultant.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4">10. Governing Law and Disputes</h2>
          <p>These Terms and Conditions are governed by French law. In the event of a dispute, an amicable resolution will be sought first. Failing that, the courts of Lyon, France shall have sole jurisdiction.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-white/30 text-xs border-t border-white/10 pt-6">In force since 1 January 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
